<p>And speaking of distractions, your home is also filled with temptations that may veer your focus away from your work. The television and other electronic media such as radio, game gizmos and others and print media will surely lure you away from your work. But your greatest enemy is your best friend – the internet.</p>

<p>Keep a private place away from distractions plus a strong will and determination to accomplish your tasks are essential to fight off these temptations.</p>

